// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0287 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: d84d6d49-cb11-5825-a2b9-bd936fd9d985

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
